news.title: Laser Hair Removal Market to Reach $7.7 billion, Globally, by 2035 at 18.3% CAGR: Allied Market Research
news.description: Wilmington, Delaware, Feb. 26, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Allied Market Research published a report, titled, "Laser Hair Removal Market by Type (Alexandrite laser hair removal, Diode laser hair removal, Others), by Gender (Male, Female), by Age group (13 to 29 Years, 30 to 54 Years, 55 to 69 Years), by End User (Hospitals, Clinic, Others): Global Opportunity Analysis and Industry Forecast, 2025-2035". According to the report, the "laser hair removal market" was valued at $1 billion in 2023, and is estimated to reach $7.7 billion by 2035, growing at a CAGR of 18.3% from 2025 to 2035.
